credit_line: Gift of George Alfred Cluett, Class of 1896
title: Floor lamp with floral design
description: cylindrical shaft with brass bulbous knob in center; upper part composed of a cluster of polychromed flowers in green and red, and gilded metal bobeche in the form of a crown; tripod scroll base is further decorated with floral ornamentation; candelabras have already been electrified
